data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT!!! Welcome to 215 Derusso Street Houma, LA 70364. This Gorgeous 5 year old, 3BR 2BA, CUSTOM built home by Travis Buquet Home Builders, LLC awaits it's new owner. This home boasts an open but split floorplan with large bedrooms and an even bigger, more elegant master bedroom and master bathroom. The master bathroom has a large jetted tub with a separate shower and two separate sinks making it easy to share. This home does not have any carpet with the majority of the home having a beautiful wood-look luxury vinyl. The bathrooms have ceramic tile. The kitchen is spacious and open to the living area with stainless steel appliances and a nice pantry. If you like to cook with natural gas, this home has what you are looking for! The exterior of the home is all brick with an attached covered patio that also has a natural gas spigot. The backyard is also spacious with a wooden fence surrounding it for privacy. Even more appealing is the fact that the backyard has RV/Boat access. The large garage and driveway offers plenty of parking. This home also has a tankless water heater. Call your favorite REALTOR to see all that this home has to offer!!! (Flood zone designation and square foot measurements of the home and property to be verified by buyer.)
